                                .contentBox_table_block
                                    .contentBox_table_blockL
                                        h3 お名前
                                        span *
                                    .contentBox_table_blockR
                                        input(type='text', name="お名前" id="name" class="text-field" v-model='name' v-on='change:onBlogCheckName' v-validate='required')
                                        .validation
                                            span(v-if='validation.name.required && !blogCheckFlg.name') お名前を入力してください
